title: [Vornavian Coast, The Hills]
description: Several large boulders are scattered about near the path here, providing many cracks, crevices, nooks, and crannies where small animals and lizards can hide.  Gaps in the boulders to the east and west are wide enough to allow passage.  The path continues to the northeast and the southwest.
paths: Obvious paths: northeast, east, southwest, west
